body.name: DIY Computer Motherboard Case | Chassis Cooling Frame | Stackable PC Computer Case | Open Chassis Support Bracket with Good Heat Dissipation
features: ℛFashion Appearance: Computer Motherboard Case Rack allows you to fully experience the fun of DIY. The chassis needs to be DIY installed by yourself. This is easy to disassemble.
ℛGood Heat Dissipation: The Chassis Motherboard Bracket supports ATX power supplies. It adopts an open frame design with good and quick heat dissipation.
ℛPortable Frame: The Metal Air Water Cooling Fan Stand supports 2 expansion mechanical hard drive bays or 4 SSD bays. It has enough space for a 305*330/330*330MM motherboard.
ℛBroad Compatibility: Stackable Open Chassis Rack is compaatible with ATX, ATX, and ITX motherboards and supports discrete graphics cards. It is widely compatible.
ℛReliable and Stable: The PC Motherboard Case Frame is made of aluminum-type material, which is sturdy and durable. It has a stable vertical structure.
body.description: Description1: Product size: length 435*width 340*height 195, the product uses two kinds of 0.8MM/1.5MM thick SPCC materials, and the surfaces are sprayed with black sand powder.2: Support ATX supply, support 300MM long supply.3: Support EATX motherboard 305*330, 330*330MM, support ATX, ATX, and ITX motherboard.4: The height of the CPU cooler is 165MM (stacking can support 177MM).5: The back supports 1 12CM fan or 120 water cooling; the front can support 3 12CM fans or 1 240 or 1 360 water drain.6: Supports up to 2 mechanical hard disks and 3 solid-state hard disk fixed positions.7: It can stand, lie and stack, suitable for different scenarios, portable and mobile.SpecificationsMaterial: steel plateSize: about 435*340*195mm/17.13*13.34*7.68inch(LxWxH)Colour: BlackFunction: portable open computer DIY casePacking listChassis frame*1Wrench*1Power-on line*1Screw bag*1
